headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Palantir Stock Jumps as Listing Heads to Nasdaq
summary: The S&P 500 fell 1.3% on Friday, Nov. 15, after the Fed chair struck a cautious tone about additional rate cuts and a report showed strong retail sales in October.
